overview: Tempo is predicted to be genuine. RIVER JEWEL went nicely in a blanket finish in town last start. Inferior race here and her prior personal best rating was 2nd up last campaign. Is an excellent chance. AS IT LIES is poised to significantly advance 3rd up off two similar ratings 2nds thus far, this campaign. 4th up last campaign she won her maiden. NO VEECAT resumes off a sound maiden win when the market expected it. Must presume some natural improvement into this. JOSEPHINE SEA next best.
